node.text:
Today is World Day Against Trafficking in Persons, and I wanted to highlight the incredible work that my friend @timballard89 and his amazing organization @ourrescue are doing…

Tim has dedicated his life to freeing children all over the world from lives of slavery. That’s where his mission led him to begin O.U.R, and I’m so thankful that we were able to connect a few years ago…

We had the incredible opportunity to help produce their documentary “Operation Toussaint” that has helped show the amazing work they’re doing every day shining a very bright light in the darkest parts of the world. The work that Tim and his team are doing is SO important, and I’m honored and grateful to do whatever possible to help in their mission. 

Head to their profile at @ourrescue to see how you can #RiseUp and help #EndHumanTrafficking!!!

node.title: Are you ready to #RiseUp for children?!?

node.text: As an entrepreneur, do you struggle going on vacations..? If so, this message is for you! I made this video a few years ago, but thought it was appropriate to post, now that we’re half way through the summer… in hopes to remind you that you’re not weird… you’re an Entrepreneur, and that’s ok!!

node.text:
The last 12 months have been hard for many…

But for those who were at FHL, we were prepared… One month before the lockdown, we had 5,000 ‘Funnel Hackers’ together at FHL, and @TonyRobbins predicted what was about to happen…

We just released an “After Movie” from FHL 2020, and it INSTANTLY gets me back in state to continue to create… to work… to serve!!! I can only hope it does the same for you :)

node.title: This is the true story of the moment I was so close to losing it all 💯

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Russell Brunson on September 01, 2021. May be an image of 1 person and text that says 'Russell Brunson @russellbrunson 208-231-3797 208-231 It's September 1st. You have 4 months left in 2021. That's 121 days, 2.904 hours, or 174,240 minutes. Plenty of time for you to learn a new skill, change your routine, increase your income, lose weight, gain muscle, etc. Get after it. DOUBLE TAP to affirm!'.

node.text:
No matter what you’re working towards… you have time to accomplish it!!!

Today brings you a fresh start at working towards your goals… it’s now up to you to put in the hard work and stay dedicated!

Because the next season of YOU is about to start… but the big question is, are you ready?!

Double tap and let me know!!!

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Russell Brunson on August 31, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'HOW WE'RE TAUGHT TO MEASURE SUCCESS SALARY JOB TITLE A BETTER SCALE MENTAL HEALTH FREE TIME INCOME PHYSICAL HEALTH IMPACT @RUSSELLBRUNSON LIKING WHAT YOU DO'.

node.text:
Success isn’t just measured by your salary or job title…

Stop focusing on the money and start focusing on how you are mentally, physically, the impact you're making, the amount of time you have to do what you truly love… because THAT’S what really matters.

Give me a “🙌” if you’re with me on this one!!!

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Russell Brunson on August 30, 2021. May be an image of 1 person and text that says 'Russell Brunson @russellbrunson 208-231-3797 The 5 stages of an online business: $100 profit: $1,000 profit: $10,000 profit: $100,000 profit: $1,000,000 profit: Which level are you on?'.

node.text:
This game is all about leveling up!!! No matter what stage you’re at in your journey, each one is an accomplishment…let it serve as motivation to move towards the next!

So, which level are you on?! 👇

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Russell Brunson on August 29, 2021 tagging @daveswoodward. May be an image of 2 people and indoor.

node.text:
Today I’m grateful for @daveswoodward - he’s one of my closest friends, he’s someone I look up to as a father and husband, his faith in God is unshakable, and  he’s spent the last few years supporting me, and this crazy community of entrepreneurs (we call Funnel Hackers) at a level that no one else has matched. 

Dave - I’m grateful for you, your life and your example. So glad to have you here on this the crazy journey with me! 

… and come on, that new beard is pretty dang cool !!!

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Russell Brunson on August 27, 2021 tagging @russellbrunson. May be an image of 1 person and text that says 'Russell Brunson @russellb @russellbrunson 208 3797 You wouldn't plant a seed and then dig it up every few minutes to see ifit it has grown...'.

node.text:
Having faith in yourself is what will get you through this journey :) 
So stop questioning your hard work and your decisions. Have faith that you are where you need to be right now, and keep working hard to move forward :)

Comment me a “❤️” if this resonated with you!!!

Photo by Russell Brunson on August 26, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'Things that I always tell entrepreneurs...'.

node.text:
I’ve always said that we’ve been placed on this earth with a calling from God to fulfill…

He has given us unique talents, abilities, and things we can do. We just need to figure out how to take those talents and use them to serve the people that we’ve been called to help.

Give me a “🙏🙏🙏” if you agree!!!

Photo by Russell Brunson on August 26, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'Comment me a if you agree.'.
Photo shared by Russell Brunson on August 25, 2021 tagging @russellbrunson. May be a cartoon of standing and text that says 'HAPPINESS IS A STATE OF MIND 3 1. 2 @RUSSELLBRUNSON @RUSSELL ろ'.

node.text:
Something we all could remember ;)

You have the ability to be happy at any time no matter what’s going on around you!!!

Happiness is a choice, a way of living… so instead of viewing happiness as an emotion, view it as a state of mind… I promise it’s a game changer :)

If you wait around for something to make you happy, you may never experience true happiness… 

Because it’s always inside of you, you just have to remember to bring it out!!!

Who are you funnel hacking? Let me know in the comments!!!

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Russell Brunson on August 23, 2021 tagging @cocalettie, and @russellbrunson. May be an image of 3 people, people standing and text that says 'Russell Brunson @russellbrunson 208-231-3797 You can make money by accident, but you can't get wealthy by accident.'.

node.text:
Something we all need to hear…

If you want to be wealthy, you have to put in the work… because it’s not going to happen by accident!!! It takes time, hard work, commitment, and belief in yourself and your mission to make it happen… 

In the end, the money truly doesn’t matter… but it's what gives us the freedom to spend time with the things that do matter!

And the moment we have that freedom is the moment we're truly wealthy :)

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Russell Brunson on August 22, 2021. May be an image of 11 people, people standing and outdoors.

node.text:
We had a blast night night at the Boise fair with our little ones!! Swipe over to see is eating the largest turkey leg in the world, and Norah riding a 🐫!!! 

School starts for the kids this week, so this was our last big adventure before we get back to a schedule (and I’m not going to lie… I’m SO excited to get them all back on a normal schedule!)

node.text:
Great things take time, but getting to that next level requires focus and sacrifice...

Think about it, if you give your all for the next few years, staying completely focused on your mission and being willing to sacrifice the things that serve as distractions, you could set yourself up for the rest of your life and work to make a true impact…

Are you willing to commit to that?! For yourself, your family, for the people you’re trying to serve… let me know if you’re with me!!!

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Russell Brunson on August 19, 2021 tagging @russellbrunson. May be a Twitter screenshot of 1 person and text that says 'Russell Brunson @russellbrunson 208-231-379 Never apologize for being obsessed... Actually, you know what? VIKECK'.

node.text:
Being obsessed is what will lead you to success… so never apologize for it!!!

Don't be ashamed to spend time geeking out on whatever it is you are obsessed with and fully immersing yourself in it... because THAT is how you're going to win!

I could spend DAYS building funnels and funnel hacking because that's my obsession... and there's nothing wrong with that!!!

Positive obsession is a gift, not a behavior to be suppressed ;)

Drop a big YES if you agree!!!
